e famine was sore in the land.","year":-1707},{"id":"recMep3lksmcmffZY","ref":"Gen.43.2","text":"And it came to pass, when they had eaten up the corn which they had brought out of Egypt, their father said unto them, Go again, buy us a little food.","year":-1707},{"id":"rec2wKdqSU3ttHUsk","ref":"Gen.43.3","text":"And Judah spake unto him, saying, The man did solemnly protest unto us, saying, Ye shall not see my face, except your brother be with you.","year":-1707}]}
